{"tid":1581383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721建議大家唔好阻人清野","createTime":"2019-09-19T14:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T14:10:16.000Z","uid":118941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"834d35837d44bded611e4f2738abd0db2040a256","tid":1581383,"uid":118941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"我相信當日都一定有白衫人打人架啦，保護自己唔出去其實最好。<br />\n而且大家出去其實<span style=\"color: red;\">無意義</span>，我同你地分析一下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.出去唔還手自己受傷，還手又自己人分裂又比口實人</span><br />\n到時打贏又無著數，打輸又唔好睇，即使唔還手，都可能被人拉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.即使保護到連濃墻，都無乜意義</span><br />\n其實邊次連濃墻既野留得耐，佢地唔清我地自己都清啦，要貼新野呀嘛。<br />\n今次有佢地幫手清定比我地貼文宣過1.10，開心都黎唔切啦。<br />\n只怕佢地又清完掉落地下。辛苦清潔姐姐嬸嬸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">其實大家要出去不如佢地清完既時候先出去，幫手清理佢地掉落睇下既垃圾。<br />\n企到道德高地之餘，無人受傷，無人送頭。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n天滅中共，皇天擊殺。</span>"},{"pid":"c526267e0660444a17bd6cdae469d52698736298","tid":1581383,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"921下話？"},{"pid":"eb5ad3b896898f9cea50c2d3ca51fc0dd2be6d0a","tid":1581383,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"下年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65130b7d1dc4298a49cbec21fc14695f685db1c2","tid":1581383,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"921<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4a1343c8cef4c6112b413a22d9757da22022e2","tid":1581383,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94d26296cd28f46ebca32d4d6de68096557f6243","tid":1581383,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地